(1, 1, 'Fatburger Davie', 'Although the staff were excellent the burger was not! If I am spending $18 dollars on a burger I expect it to be a good burger. This burger was cold,no flavor and the bun was soggy. In the past I have enjoyed Fatburger but after this experience I will never be back! Much cheaper and better burgers at White Spot.', 'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipP9KrohXTvnSrTQbiW9po0afYMmSws0BeZ30WJq=w408-h272-k-no', 49.280390, -123.110680),
(1, 1, 'White Spot Dunsmuir', 'Excellent White Spot restaurant! We were served in a friendly manner and were able to order quickly and then got our food in no time. Atmosphere is warm and friendly, and it is nice that the TVs are conveniently located so no matter where you sit you can see one. Theres lots of seating, and several big booths. The only thing I would say is that I ordered a Legendary Burger, but wasnt asked if I wanted lettuce and tomato but I didnt realize it, and when I got my order I didnt know for a second what it was. But thats my only complaint, this restaurant really is great and I would definitely recommend it!', 'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipN0UiG687fSraEgjcL3vYX8tu04HrjIk5Cs0qZc=w408-h306-k-no', 49.281980, -123.113980),
(1, 1, 'Five Guys', 'I went to this place with my husband and we had a great time here! The employees were very swift and efficient! We did not have to wait long in spite of the place being crowded! The quality of their burger is top notch! And everything inside of it went amazingly together! The peanuts were an added bonus! The bathrooms were clean and hygienic! The place itself needs some tidying though.', 'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipPm9IYsFXBxMJmjSDnJl3KNEidkz2eTNApjZPQ=w408-h306-k-no', 49.281060, -123.119020),
(1, 2, 'MeeT in Gastown', 'As a Thai, from LA.  This place is legit!! Everything is really good here.  Taste super authentic.  "Very spicy" here is actually spicy, which is hard to find.  Even the drinks and desserts were great.  Nothing really to complain. We came in on Christmas day during lunch, the place was packed.  The food was a little slow, but it was worth the wait. Definitely be coming here every time I come to Vegas.', 'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOjE2RwNzKXLUV04l1olFNBxRr5vIaUSwWA_FfD=w408-h272-k-no', 49.283126, -123.104998),
(1, 2, 'Tera V Burger', 'Probably had their No Bull burger in the different variations probably more than 10 times already in the past few years. Usually on delivery and always with a smoothie. I would say I prefer it to meat burgers as a person that does eat meat. Better than Beyond Meat patties in general, but even the beyond meat burgers are prepared better than other places Ive tried. Keep at it guys!', 'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMS1x_9Eitc8KP1T0sCB3Sn8B9bSdaxzIv2PzXZ=w426-h240-k-no', 49.264274, -123.171735),
(1, 2, 'Campagnolo', 'Northern Italian menu, with pizza & housemade salumi, served under exposed bulbs.', 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/58eda1fcc534a5e94d713978/1521604810164-O8D7HHN7BV9GCY17VM01/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kAFe3081NhNr2t9KEWiap3J7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QHyNOqBUUEtDDsRWrJLTmvchaurtRArZJfSwNtuHUKiaLhdcjAPjMR3zMp3I7ofkUS6FEqR4U86UhMLLsVopb/20180208_203420.png?format=1500w', 49.285641, -123.126411),
(1, 2, 'Alibi Room', 'Heritage building with 50 taps of local & imported craft beers, plus a menu of locally sourced food.', 'https://img1.10bestmedia.com/Images/Photos/36218/p-alibi-room-vancouver-bc-canada-nightlife-search-all-nightlife-bar-dance-club-608481_54_990x660_201405311540.jpg', 49.281332299999995, -123.11451249999999),
(1, 2, 'Wakwak Burger', 'Beef burgers with standard & Japanese variations, served with fries & soft drinks through a window.', 'https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CnTAayfUMAAgSwp.jpg', 49.2843797, -123.11493),
(1, 2, 'Relish Gourmet Burgers', 'Fries well done, crispy and not greasy.', 'https://s3-media0.fl.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/ORIpp6mzxGqd6P84wb2LHg/l.jpg', 49.2680316, -123.1115966),
(1, 2, 'Roxy Burger', 'Lively locale offering creative burgers, other pub grub & nightly drink specials.', 'https://ssmscdn.yp.ca/image/resize/1f1bc05c-b66e-4343-8a7a-ed18055c6ca1/ypui-d-mp-pic-gal-lg/roxy-burger-4.jpg', 49.2833213, -123.1165826),
(1, 2, 'The Templeton', 'Jukebox-lined eatery with free-run eggs & breakfast faves, plus organic burgers & classic shakes.', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/F-Sb0qnDC6ADG7DY5SWbyMk23_L96kSMYql2VBvHUt8mivg23S0eb8luxtr3RTikI8iJXAaejQRwvNT-rAs6h0ernjA6PzdXoPsCWK92yJCs-p8MUssIk5XN', 49.2399548, -123.1394088),
(1, 2, 'Red Robin', 'Chain for gourmet burgers & boozy shakes, with other American comfort fare.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/03/da/b3/ab/red-robin-gourmet-burgers.jpg', 49.284239, -123.125749);
